Maximum Contract (25%) 
In seasons 2024-25, 2025-26, 2026-27 and 2027-28, guaranteed salary protection may be adjusted if Williamson doesn't meet certain games played or weigh-in targets. 
 
Guaranteed details: Source: @MikeVorkunov, Spotrac 
 
2025-26 details:  
Part 1: 
If Williamson passes weigh in targets through 2024-25 season, 20% guaranteed ($7,889,218) 
 
Part 2: 
If Williamson plays 41 or more games during 2024-25 season, 40% guaranteed ($15,778,436) 
If Williamson plays 51 or more games during 2024-25 season, 60% guaranteed ($23,667,654) 
If Williamson plays 61 or more games during 2024-25 season, 80% guaranteed ($31,556,872) 
 
2026-27, 2027-28: 
If all above clauses are met in a prior season, the salary will be guaranteed for the upcoming season. 
 
Other Clauses: 
Williamson weight must be less then 295 lbs *body fat will be checked
